# Summary
Metrics in Amplitude are reusable analysis objects that can be created by any member, manager, or admin, but only managers and administrators can designate them as official. Available on Growth and Enterprise plans, metrics can be created as Event Segmentation, Revenue, Formula, or Funnel types, with specific configuration options for visualization in Data Tables and Event Segmentation charts.

